1
00:00:55,200 --> 00:01:00,200
The Story of Minglan

2
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:03,159
Episode 12

3
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:08,480
Sit.

4
00:01:11,559 --> 00:01:13,599
These few days with Brothers Bai and Feng

5
00:01:13,599 --> 00:01:16,080
taking Imperial exams,

6
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:19,959
with only two gone, the whole house is suddenly

7
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:22,400
so quiet now.

8
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,519
Replying to Grandmother,

9
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,639
my mother says these next few days

10
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:26,040
she's going to abstain from bathing

11
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:27,760
and shut her doors to devote herself to prayer.

12
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:30,720
Others are not allowed to make a ruckus.

13
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:32,680
I hear Big Madam is praying to Confucius,

14
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,919
Buddhist and Taoist deities, all three at once.

15
00:01:34,919 --> 00:01:38,800
I don't know which is the divine spirit?

16
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:44,639
Your mother isn't devoted to the gods or Buddha.

17
00:01:44,639 --> 00:01:47,040
But I hear everyone in Linqi Pavilion

18
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,839
is holding a copy of the Book of Changes lately.

19
00:01:48,839 --> 00:01:50,239
Even those who are illiterate

20
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:52,440
are holding a compass and making calculations.

21
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:53,120
Who knows?

22
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:56,199
Maybe a person's life is already fated at birth.

23
00:01:56,199 --> 00:01:58,800
Noble is noble, and lowly is lowly.

24
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:01,239
No matter how you calculate, it's all useless.

25
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:04,919
Fifth Sister, who are you talking about here?

26
00:02:04,919 --> 00:02:06,639
I wasn't talking about anyone.

27
00:02:06,639 --> 00:02:08,880
Sister, we are just chatting idly

28
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:10,880
while gathered by Grandmother.

29
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:13,199
Why are you getting all upset for?

30
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:14,600
I . . .

31
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:32,160
Grandmother, actually, no matter what my mother prays for,

32
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:34,639
it's all for the sake of the whole family.

33
00:02:36,279 --> 00:02:38,759
During the time of your brothers' exam time,

34
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:40,759
we must have the family in harmony.

35
00:02:40,759 --> 00:02:44,160
You sisterhood must help your main mother

36
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:45,800
watch over the house.

37
00:02:49,119 --> 00:02:50,960
Yes.

38
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:57,320
Miss, the sun's about to go down. How about

39
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,520
Didn't I tell you? You're not allowed to mention

40
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:01,919
the word “down' these days!

41
00:03:01,919 --> 00:03:03,440
Can't you remember this?

42
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:06,160
A petty air is just petty.

43
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,039
If he can pass the exam

44
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:09,039
by abstaining from using some words,

45
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:11,880
then all the monks in the temple can be top scorers.

46
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,720
Even if this Brother passes with high marks,

47
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,759
the concubine-born sister?

48
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:17,119
She still can't social-climb her way into the ducal house!

49
00:03:17,119 --> 00:03:18,800
You…

50
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,639
How can you say such shameless words?

51
00:03:21,639 --> 00:03:23,199
Father has already said, no one was allowed

52
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:23,960
to fight over legitimate

53
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,080
or concubine line anymore at home.

54
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:29,279
The way you speak, you're disregarding Father.

55
00:03:29,279 --> 00:03:31,559
That acts again.

56
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,919
Nothing new?

57
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:35,639
Just cry then.

58
00:03:35,639 --> 00:03:36,919
After you're done crying, go tattle.

59
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:38,279
I'm not scared.

60
00:03:38,279 --> 00:03:39,679
You…

61
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:54,919
Fourth Sister, don't cry anymore.

62
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:57,759
Everyone's worried about the exam now.

63
00:03:57,759 --> 00:04:02,199
Later, if Father hears you, he might blame you.

64
00:04:50,239 --> 00:04:55,000
Sixth Miss, it's very cold. Don't catch a chill.

65
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:58,760
Xiaotao, add a cloak for Miss.

66
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:05,359
What are you looking at, Miss?

67
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:09,160
Fan House has lights on.

68
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,440
I heard it was ordered by the Duke and Duchess of Qi

69
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,440
to hang them for luck.

70
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,880
Miss.

71
00:05:15,079 --> 00:05:17,959
They all say Young Lord is loved by a million.

72
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:21,799
Other than parents, he has others thinking of him.

73
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:47,559
Brilliantly white like snow on the mountain.

74
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:52,839
Shining brightly as the moon between clouds.

75
00:06:35,320 --> 00:06:36,640
Don't worry, Mother.

76
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,760
Second Brother will be alright.

77
00:06:41,679 --> 00:06:43,640
Why isn't he coming out?

78
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:45,119
The door's not open yet.

79
00:06:45,119 --> 00:06:48,559
I know. I'm just anxious.

80
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:04,519
They're coming out.

81
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,279
Brother Bai is coming out.

82
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:14,359
You have to make an exception

83
00:07:14,359 --> 00:07:15,559
and go drink at the Fan House with me.

84
00:07:15,559 --> 00:07:17,519
Father. Mother.

85
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:19,119
Was it cold in the exam courtyard?

86
00:07:19,119 --> 00:07:22,320
Your family's waiting while scratching their ears.

87
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:26,119
What's he saying there? Hurry and come now.

88
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,640
Second Brother. Feng'er.

89
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,760
Father. Mother.

90
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:35,119
Bai'er. How did the exam go?

91
00:07:35,119 --> 00:07:36,760
Young Master. Over here.

92
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,440
Young Master.

93
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,959
Let me. How did it go, Second Brother?

94
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:44,519
I'm sure he can place it at the top!

95
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:46,880
You must be so exhausted.

96
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:49,480
I'll help you recuperate.

97
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:52,839
Let's go. Did the scholar guess it right?

98
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:54,519
You've only tested for three days

99
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:56,279
and you've thinned out three rounds.

100
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:00,000
Were the exam topics

101
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,559
very different from what you studied for?

102
00:08:02,559 --> 00:08:05,119
Your mother worries so much these days.

103
00:08:05,559 --> 00:08:07,760
I'm talking to you.

104
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:10,399
Mother. Let me catch my breath first.

105
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:12,600
I was holed up in that shell of a room for three days.

106
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,640
I need to get some fresh air.

107
00:08:14,679 --> 00:08:17,519
Alright, then. Get some air. Let's go.

108
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:19,079
Get in the carriage.

109
00:08:51,799 --> 00:08:55,039
What did you see? You're so happy.

110
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:57,440
I didn't get to see Mother

111
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,239
for three days and I've missed you.

112
00:08:59,239 --> 00:09:01,679
Now I'm heading home.

113
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:04,080
I don't know why but I just feel happy.

114
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:11,719
Your mouth is growing sweeter.

115
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:37,359
Xueniang's man Chiwu was sent off

116
00:09:37,359 --> 00:09:39,359
for Yangzhou by Mistress Lin today,

117
00:09:39,359 --> 00:09:42,000
saying it's to procure some items.

118
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:45,119
Such timing she picks.

119
00:09:45,119 --> 00:09:47,239
The entire family is waiting for exam results

120
00:09:47,239 --> 00:09:48,799
and there's no room to think about anything else,

121
00:09:48,799 --> 00:09:51,039
so no one will notice her.

122
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:53,679
Do we go see your aunt later today?

123
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:54,960
Not later today, right now.

124
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:57,799
You go to the inn right away.

125
00:09:57,799 --> 00:10:00,440
Tell my aunt the snake's already shown itself.

126
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,000
As long as she follows that Chiwu,

127
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:04,520
she won't need to worry that she won't find some clues.

128
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,320
Miss, you wanted me to pretend

129
00:10:06,599 --> 00:10:07,280
like I was sending your aunt

130
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:08,239
back to Yangzhou secretly late at night,

131
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:11,880
and installing your aunt at the inn.

132
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:14,679
At the time, I didn't know what you were trying to do.

133
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:16,919
Now you know then?

134
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:21,840
Fishing requires a hook and a bait.

135
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:25,799
Now, we just wait for news.

136
00:11:04,679 --> 00:11:07,840
This morning's incense is burning so beautifully.

137
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,880
Great, like a lotus flower!

138
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:12,440
That's a great auspicious sign from above.

139
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:15,000
I bet our Bai'er must have placed at the top!

140
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:19,000
Yes, yes, top placement.

141
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:21,239
Why is Ru'er still not out yet?

142
00:11:21,239 --> 00:11:23,359
We've finally made it through to the results posting

143
00:11:23,359 --> 00:11:24,919
and she's still so lazy?

144
00:11:24,919 --> 00:11:27,440
Hurry and rush Fifth Miss!

145
00:11:28,599 --> 00:11:30,400
Winning or losing is at one stroke.

146
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,719
Bai'er must win for me.

147
00:11:31,719 --> 00:11:33,559
Best if my son places at the top,

148
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:36,239
and that little rabbit's name falls to the bottom.

149
00:11:36,239 --> 00:11:37,200
Then I'll see—eek!

150
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:39,679
Big Madam! Big Madam!

151
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:44,200
You put too much power into that stroke.

152
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:44,880
It's off-scale.

153
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:51,039
You have something on your mind to break through.

154
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:54,039
If you can't write well, rest a bit.

155
00:11:54,719 --> 00:11:56,719
I can write well.

156
00:11:57,479 --> 00:12:00,320
You're worried about the Young Lord's result.

157
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,679
How can you write well?

158
00:12:06,559 --> 00:12:11,400
N-No. I I'm not.

159
00:12:12,159 --> 00:12:14,200
I've lived to such an age,

160
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:18,239
at least I can tell about these things.

161
00:12:18,239 --> 00:12:20,039
The night before the big exam,

162
00:12:20,039 --> 00:12:21,880
Young Lord came

163
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:23,280
under pretext of paying respects

164
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:24,479
to come present gifts here.

165
00:12:24,479 --> 00:12:25,719
But in reality,

166
00:12:25,719 --> 00:12:28,840
he was just trying to send a gift to you.

167
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:31,919
That's putting a louse on top of a bald head.

168
00:12:31,919 --> 00:12:33,159
So obvious!

169
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:41,520
You're the flesh on my heart.

170
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:43,880
Of course I want you

171
00:12:43,880 --> 00:12:47,080
to have the best match in the world.

172
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:52,960
Qi Yuanruo is a great person and his family is great too.

173
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:56,719
Just that the family is too great

174
00:12:56,719 --> 00:12:57,599
and the parents are strict.

175
00:12:58,119 --> 00:12:59,039
If you go over there,

176
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:03,400
first, you may not rise to be the main wife,

177
00:13:04,919 --> 00:13:08,239
and second, even if you rise to be the main wife,

178
00:13:08,479 --> 00:13:10,479
your days will still just be full of suffering.

179
00:13:12,039 --> 00:13:14,440
On this, you'll have to be clear-minded.

180
00:13:19,159 --> 00:13:22,359
Princess Pingning is so proud and arrogant.

181
00:13:22,719 --> 00:13:24,440
Her prospects are far-reaching

182
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,599
and too rich to be a good match.

183
00:13:26,719 --> 00:13:28,239
Your granddaughter understands all that.

184
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,599
It's just a bit hard to take.

185
00:13:44,919 --> 00:13:46,919
Big Madam rushed out and wasn't careful,

186
00:13:46,919 --> 00:13:49,440
so she slipped and sprained her foot.

187
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,880
She's fussing about calling a physician here.

188
00:13:52,919 --> 00:13:55,159
The results are posted.

189
00:13:55,159 --> 00:13:56,320
Whether you go see it or not,

190
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:58,960
the rankings won't change.

191
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,799
Old Madam is right.

192
00:14:00,799 --> 00:14:01,840
Master said that

193
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:04,039
let Fifth Miss go and have a look.

194
00:14:04,039 --> 00:14:05,280
But Big Madam just

195
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:06,960
insists on going personally.

196
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:09,039
She's fussing about it now.

197
00:14:09,119 --> 00:14:10,239
Ming'er.

198
00:14:10,239 --> 00:14:13,080
You accompany your Fifth Sister for the trip.

199
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:14,719
The Minister does not find it convenient to leave.

200
00:14:14,919 --> 00:14:17,280
He needs to send a messenger,

201
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:19,359
and you're my messenger.

202
00:14:20,479 --> 00:14:22,159
Go take a look at the grandsons' result

203
00:14:22,159 --> 00:14:23,479
on behalf of the grandmother.

204
00:14:23,479 --> 00:14:24,479
That's reasonable and proper.

205
00:14:30,679 --> 00:14:31,640
Thank you, Grandmother.

206
00:14:51,239 --> 00:14:53,119
Since the old days, Bianjing has had the custom

207
00:14:53,119 --> 00:14:54,159
of picking out son-in-laws before the posts.

208
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,159
Those people are waiting eagerly for the day

209
00:14:56,159 --> 00:14:57,599
the results are posted.

210
00:14:57,599 --> 00:14:58,799
Watching outside the exam courtyard,

211
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,359
seeing who passed,

212
00:15:00,359 --> 00:15:01,520
and they snatch him into their own carriage!

213
00:15:01,799 --> 00:15:03,280
Thus forcing him to marry their own daughter!

214
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,559
We must be careful so our Second Son

215
00:15:05,559 --> 00:15:07,039
isn't snatched away.

216
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:10,400
Those people are mostly town peddlers,

217
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,840
merchants of the land.

218
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:13,000
Don't mention merchants again!

219
00:15:18,679 --> 00:15:21,239
A merchant is one thing.

220
00:15:21,239 --> 00:15:25,280
But Second Son's temper.

221
00:15:25,280 --> 00:15:27,440
You know,

222
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,039
if he's bent on being stubborn,

223
00:15:29,039 --> 00:15:31,039
I don't know who he will pick,

224
00:15:31,039 --> 00:15:32,760
and

225
00:15:32,760 --> 00:15:35,080
it will affect his future career as an official.

226
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:39,599
He's keeping a singing girl outside.

227
00:15:39,599 --> 00:15:40,359
Did he think about

228
00:15:40,359 --> 00:15:42,359
his government career then?

229
00:15:47,679 --> 00:15:48,799
If we can get our Second Son

230
00:15:48,799 --> 00:15:50,479
to chase that woman away, that will be great.

231
00:15:51,479 --> 00:15:53,719
But with his temperament?

232
00:15:54,479 --> 00:15:56,239
He surely won't be willing.

233
00:15:56,239 --> 00:15:58,119
He dares?

234
00:16:00,239 --> 00:16:01,559
Whether he passes this exam or not,

235
00:16:01,760 --> 00:16:02,479
he must separate from

236
00:16:02,479 --> 00:16:03,280
that woman regardless.

237
00:16:04,479 --> 00:16:05,479
If he refuses,

238
00:16:05,479 --> 00:16:06,520
I will break his legs.

239
00:16:08,239 --> 00:16:09,960
Don't fret, My Lord.

240
00:16:11,039 --> 00:16:12,200
He's become

241
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:14,320
more mature lately.

242
00:16:16,520 --> 00:16:17,640
And also,

243
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:19,840
no one passes the exam on first try.

244
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:23,239
If he didn't pass today,

245
00:16:23,239 --> 00:16:24,320
don't you scold him.

246
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,000
Second Brother!

247
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:43,200
Your entire family has mobilized.

248
00:16:43,479 --> 00:16:45,159
They're so scared if you made to the top of the roster,

249
00:16:45,159 --> 00:16:45,960
their brother will be snatched away.

250
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:47,559
Even the younger sisters are here as your guards.

251
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:55,840
Here, here.

252
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:01,200
That man seems quite good.

253
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:03,799
Handsome in appearance and a great air about him.

254
00:17:04,079 --> 00:17:05,680
He's got that unique air

255
00:17:05,680 --> 00:17:07,119
about him.

256
00:17:07,479 --> 00:17:09,119
If he passes,

257
00:17:09,119 --> 00:17:09,800
Brother Wang,

258
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:11,680
you must not try to fight me for him.

259
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:15,599
Landlord Lu, you take him all you want.

260
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:17,479
Why?

261
00:17:18,319 --> 00:17:19,479
He's Gu Tingye.

262
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:20,280
I will not

263
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:22,040
fight you for him.

264
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:24,280
That's actually him?

265
00:17:24,280 --> 00:17:26,959
That charming vanguard.

266
00:17:26,959 --> 00:17:28,880
Beguiling conqueror of the peony.

267
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:31,439
My daughter? I'd rather keep her with me forever

268
00:17:31,439 --> 00:17:33,920
than to have him ruin her!

269
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:35,920
That's true!

270
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:39,319
Did you hear that?

271
00:17:39,319 --> 00:17:41,160
No one wants to find one like me

272
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,319
for their son-in-law.

273
00:17:47,119 --> 00:17:48,719
