687
00:34:19,560 --> 00:34:20,879
Wine, wine.

688
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:23,120
You said it well!

689
00:34:31,239 --> 00:34:32,439
Yes.

690
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:35,679
There's a matter

691
